  + [spec_006] is develop narrow math tools only when repeated inquiry reveals a concrete classification or closure need
  + [spec_007] is record every proof-shaping result as SOP artifacts before summarizing or moving lanes
  + [spec_008] is run project-local Git reflection after major open locks or large project deltas
  + [spec_009] is separate narrative, model, computational experiment, formal theorem, and proof-status claims in all downstream documents
